RACE.RACE_TEXT: MEADOWLANDS RACE 1 1 1/16M Turf CR: 61. Maiden Special Weight Purse 45450. FOR REGISTERED NEW JERSEY BREDS MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 123 lbs. (Rail at 17 feet).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: DESERT PASSION vied two wide for command, dueled two wide entering the far turn, held a short lead turning for home, dug in gamely inside of DUCHESS OF DESTIN in the final furlong and prevailed determinedly. DUCHESS OF DESTIN stalked close up three wide, bid three wide entering the far turn, dueled with the winner, dug in gamely outside of that rival passing the furlong marker and battled gamely to the finish. LOOKINGFORTREASURE checked sharply entering the first turn, then tracked on the inside, was shuffled back a bit entering the far turn, came two wide into the lane and rallied mildly for third. LILY THE KID bumped at the start, raced three or four wide off the pace, bid four wide entering the far turn, then chased and was outkicked for the show spot. FIRST REIGN raced off the pace, came three wide into the lane and gained mildly outside. LADY TRIXMEISTER raced off the pace with an inside trip and lacked a rally. BABY CAKES was fractious in the gate, vied inside for the lead, dueled into the far turn, then faded. WHISKEY AND RAIN stalked two wide, chased three wide on the far turn and faded. DIXIE LARK bumped and steadied at the start and was outrun. ME SO LUCKY was off a bit slow, raced three wide off the pace and did not factor.
